  "detailed_description": "VThree is the low poly, atmospheric, fast paced first person platformer you didn’t know you needed. Run, jump, and wall jump your way to the top of the leader boards, snagging platinum achievements along the way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCome join the community Discord https://discord.gg/nGXS8RR to provide input, ideas, and feedback. VThree's most recent release was a ground up rewrite addressing a host of changes requested by the community - we listen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPresently in Early Access with an anticipated exit from EA on January 17th.",
  "about_the_game": "VThree is the low poly, atmospheric, fast paced first person platformer you didn’t know you needed. Run, jump, and wall jump your way to the top of the leader boards, snagging platinum achievements along the way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCome join the community Discord https://discord.gg/nGXS8RR to provide input, ideas, and feedback. VThree's most recent release was a ground up rewrite addressing a host of changes requested by the community - we listen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPresently in Early Access with an anticipated exit from EA on January 17th.",
